PrecisRegulations Amending the UNITED NATIONS ANGOLA REGULATIONS by freezing all funds belonging to the National Union for the Total Independence of Angola (UNITA), prohibiting the sale, export, supply or shipping of mining equipment to any person in Angola, and by prohibiting the importation from Angola of all diamonds that do not have a certificate of origin issued by the Government of Unity and National Reconciliation of Angola.

precis:
Regulations Amending the UNITED NATIONS ANGOLA REGULATIONS by freezing all
funds belonging to the National Union for the Total Independence of Angola
(UNITA), prohibiting the sale, export, supply or shipping of mining
equipment to any person in Angola, and by prohibiting the importation from
Angola of all diamonds that do not have a certificate of origin issued by
the Government of Unity and National Reconciliation of Angola.
